{"tid":1472203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"表姐住係澳洲，外媒負評愈嚟愈多，澳洲三大台都係","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:45:16.000Z","uid":257447,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22b1f0581e32980d563e700012a25bfc20f89a65","tid":1472203,"uid":257447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"要諗諗辦法處理，同埋文宣都要諗下計呀！！！<br />\n特別明顯係琴日機場嘅情況令到評分惡化<br />\n<br />\n我屋企人其實好支持大家嘅升級同埋行動，特別係我老豆<br />\n我覺得我地再係咁真係會令到外國會愈嚟愈反向發展，唔再支持我地<br />\n<br />\n再者我真係都覺得哩排啲文宣少咗好多，攻勢冇咁勁，我明大家累，但都要撐住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋仲有犧牲左嘅同路人<br />\n俾狗拉咗嘅同路人<br />\n依家就話攰，瞓覺嗰陣瞓得着咩？個心過意得去咩？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">以下附上新聞片，同埋我屋企嘅對話圖</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108878629136279/posts/2897112976979483?s=100012799118422&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108878629136279%2Fposts%2F2897112976979483%3Fs%3D100012799118422%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=9a840cac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108878629136279/posts/2897112976979483?s=100012799118422&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmkUwaH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmkUwaH.png&h=d366b771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgDu4vK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgDu4vK.png&h=65b781f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f74d223607297314df351bc2e69d00b176038a08","tid":1472203,"uid":290973,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:26:35.000Z","msg":"澳洲出名多支那人<br />\n媒體一直都親中"},{"pid":"1b6aeb03de0cdf8609d75d40039a3d856d3c0221","tid":1472203,"uid":257447,"like":1,"dislike":1